{"tid":1776424,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"攬炒罷工罷課嘅一個關鍵問題","createTime":"2019-12-09T13:52:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-12-10T00:19:49.000Z","uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"64f4762d703c32e5e2073071961a7224120f34fe","tid":1776424,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:52:51.000Z","msg":"首先講攬炒: <br />\n經濟衰退 -&gt; 放大陸人買嘢<br />\n更多紅色資本落係香港扎根再請大陸仔<br />\n但攬炒首當其衝嘅都係本地小商店，其次外資，假設黃色經濟圈係成功，咁攬炒就係殺藍換紅嘅機會，對家維穩力度就更大<br />\n<br />\n罷工: <br />\n要兼顧口停手停<br />\n要睇實大陸人黎取代<br />\n終究有人要供樓<br />\n冇後台硬淨嘅工會，不過呢個問題係有機會解決到，只要黃色經濟圈夠大夠集中<br />\n<br />\n罷課: <br />\nGPA<br />\n唔好以為 GPA 係浮雲，啲大行 graduate program，intern，master 全部都睇到實一實<br />\n一個 game theory 黎，你罷課我唔罷 -&gt; 我高分 -&gt; outperform 你<br />\n會有人駁罷課會温書咪唔影響 GPA ，但係你睇下鄰國學生 share source 比自己友個網絡係幾大，prof 又鄰國人。香港人上連登 r 下 source 都比人屌柒。罷課時期會唔會有集中嘅 source 幫下大學生(also 中學生)？<br />\n<br />\n我預呢個 post 實有人屌分化屌五毛失敗主義。不過問題依然存在<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fc2c9e8f7e4c488da268204c38968d762092766","tid":1776424,"uid":36383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:54:35.000Z","msg":"集思廣益"},{"pid":"2f25c6cc3251bc30fa61b756483a9966ffc04a3b","tid":1776424,"uid":238275,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:55:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/kucMp8c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FkucMp8c.png&h=33c96d8f&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"ba32ab2d48bc11783a04139c22778d93329fc51d","tid":1776424,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T13:56:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daa485035070dd4ec038d191889b1de0493e3e8e","tid":1776424,"uid":47149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-12-09T15:45:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0e95ac1a982f05cf454ec0f9d53388bb5acd5527","